bgVids.desc: Highlights of Sentinels controller player 'Jared zombs Gitlin' from a match that took place on Wednesday, September 15th, 2021 at 1:00PM EDT in group D of the Valorant Champions Tour Stage 3: Masters Berlin. These clips are taken from their game against G2 on Icebox, which was map 1 in the best of 3 series. Although heavily favoured to win this series, it ended in a shocking 0-2 loss for the Sentinels, in which Jared did not play very well, causing fans to make a compilation of his best moments in the match to make him feel better.
